7 April 2017Government will today brief the media on the developments around today s protest march. Minister of Communications, Ms Ayanda Dlodlo supported by Ministers in the Justice, Crime Prevention and Security Cluster (JCPS) will lead the media briefing. The briefing will take place as follows:Date: Today, Friday, 07 April 2017 Time: 17h00 Venue: GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Hatfield, PretoriaNB: Member of the media in Cape Town can join the media briefing via a video link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament. Enquiries: Phumla Williams 083 501 0139 Donald Liphoko 082 901 0766Issued by GCIS on behalf of The Ministry of Communication